<p>As for preparing coffee with saffron, this is evidence of earning a lot of profit and money in the coming period, while whoever dreams that he prepares coffee and drinks it alone indicates that he prefers to stay away from people.  Because he wants to live in isolation.  Making <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-صنع-القهوة-لابن-سيرين?page=51" > coffee </a> means moving to a new place or planning to travel soon.  .</p>
