<p><span></span></p>
<p>As for those who dream that their appearance is very bad and dirty and they come out of prison, this is a sign that they will be able to control all aspects of their lives, even if they are unhappy in their lives, their affairs will. improve and they will reach many good news.</p>
<h2><strong>A person's release from prison in a dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></strong></h2>
<p>The great scholar <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> explained that <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/الخروج-من-السجن-في-المنام?page=388" > release from prison </a> means that the dreamer will receive a lot of good news that will cause a series of urgent changes in his life.  He has been through for a long time and his life in general will pass.</p>
<p>As for those who were imprisoned for a long time by illness, their release from prison indicates that they will recover from their illness in the coming period and return to their normal lives.  That he tries as much as possible to overcome all the crises in his life, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> also realized that the dreamer is surrounded by a number of hypocrites, so he needs to be careful.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
