<p><span></span></p>
<p>As for those who dream that they are trying to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/الخروج-من-السجن-في-المنام?page=388" > get out of prison </a> and they are surrounded by dogs in all directions, this indicates that there are many hypocrites around the dreamer who are trying to spoil his life by plotting and conspiring and entering. a lot of trouble.</p>
<p>And <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> says that the release of the prisoner is evidence of sincere repentance and closeness to God Almighty to forgive him all his sins.</p>
