</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>If a single woman sees that she is stealing from a store based on the orders of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > someone </a> , this means that she is listening to the orders of others and never makes decisions on her own.</p>
